{"componentChunkName":"component---src-template-blog-post-template-js","path":"/blog/about-canvas-ctx-createLinearGradient/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<p>我有一个需求: 把图片连带它的 css 样式画到 canvas 中, 但搜索了一番, 似乎不能直接实现. 如果这个图片的 css 样式比较简单, 可以尝试 <a href=\"https://developers.weixin.qq.com/miniprogram/dev/extended/component-plus/wxml-to-canvas.html\">wxml-to-canvas</a>, 但它支持的 css 样式比较少, 所以不能处理相对复杂的情况.</p>\n<p>另一种方法是用 canvas 的 api 把图片的 css 样式逐个画出来, 下图最右边是原图, 第一二两幅分别由 css 和 canvas api 实现, 并不完全一样, 因为我偷懒, 但基本一致.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; color: grey; margin: 0; padding: 0\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/bb61bf84330fe8b35c88de7f4b3bd677/ba381/canvas_css.webp 200w,\n/static/bb61bf84330fe8b35c88de7f4b3bd677/7f61c/canvas_css.webp 400w,\n/static/bb61bf84330fe8b35c88de7f4b3bd677/d00b9/canvas_css.webp 800w,\n/static/bb61bf84330fe8b35c88de7f4b3bd677/92f8c/canvas_css.webp 1200w,\n/static/bb61bf84330fe8b35c88de7f4b3bd677/fad48/canvas_css.webp 1600w,\n/static/bb61bf84330fe8b35c88de7f4b3bd677/2ac07/canvas_css.webp 1842w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/bb61bf84330fe8b35c88de7f4b3bd677/e07e9/canvas_css.jpg 200w,\n/static/bb61bf84330fe8b35c88de7f4b3bd677/066f9/canvas_css.jpg 400w,\n/static/bb61bf84330fe8b35c88de7f4b3bd677/4b190/canvas_css.jpg 800w,\n/static/bb61bf84330fe8b35c88de7f4b3bd677/e5166/canvas_css.jpg 1200w,\n/static/bb61bf84330fe8b35c88de7f4b3bd677/b17f8/canvas_css.jpg 1600w,\n/static/bb61bf84330fe8b35c88de7f4b3bd677/3cb25/canvas_css.jpg 1842w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/bb61bf84330fe8b35c88de7f4b3bd677/4b190/canvas_css.jpg\"\n          alt=\"canvas css\"\n          title=\"canvas css\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>看起来有点复杂, 其实主要是通过 <code class=\"language-text\">ctx.createLinearGradient()</code> 创建线性渐变的阴影, 再把这个阴影 fill 到画布中实现. <code class=\"language-text\">ctx.createLinearGradient()</code> 接收两个座标点作为参数, 该方法返回 CanvasGradient 对象.</p>\n<p>两个座标点连成一条虚构的直线, 接着使用 CanvasGradient 对象在这条直线上添加渐变颜色:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> gradient <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createLinearGradient</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\ngradient<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addColorStop</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"grey\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\ngradient<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addColorStop</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"transparent\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>假设这条直线的长度是 x, 这段代码的意思是在距离 (0, 0) 这个点 0.1x 的位置设置 grey 这个颜色, 从这个位置开始渐变, 渐变至 transparent 这个颜色, 渐变的距离是从 0.1x 到 0.5x, 由于没有其他渐变颜色, 所以从 0.5x 到 x 这段距离保持为 transparent 这个颜色.</p>\n<p>颜色沿着这条直线发生渐变, 而任何一条垂直于这条直线的直线上, 所有颜色都是一样.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; color: grey; margin: 0; padding: 0\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/c4227bdaf265e07dbb5d2f2b0fb83580/ba381/linear_gradient.webp 200w,\n/static/c4227bdaf265e07dbb5d2f2b0fb83580/7f61c/linear_gradient.webp 400w,\n/static/c4227bdaf265e07dbb5d2f2b0fb83580/b0a15/linear_gradient.webp 500w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/c4227bdaf265e07dbb5d2f2b0fb83580/e07e9/linear_gradient.jpg 200w,\n/static/c4227bdaf265e07dbb5d2f2b0fb83580/066f9/linear_gradient.jpg 400w,\n/static/c4227bdaf265e07dbb5d2f2b0fb83580/41099/linear_gradient.jpg 500w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/c4227bdaf265e07dbb5d2f2b0fb83580/41099/linear_gradient.jpg\"\n          alt=\"linear gradient\"\n          title=\"linear gradient\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>最左边通过 css 实现的图片, 其中的多个渐变阴影并不垂直或平行于图片的两边, 这种情况下, 这条虚构的直线也不应该垂直于图片的两边, 所以在确定 <code class=\"language-text\">ctx.createLinearGradient()</code> 的参数时需要进行简单的三角形边角计算.</p>\n<p>可以观察到处理后的图片其色彩饱和度及对比度都发生了变化, 这是通过 ctx.filter 实现, 但小程序似乎不支持 ctx.filter(). ctx.filter 和 css 的 filter 类似.</p>\n<p>通过以下 api, canvas 还能实现类似于 css 的 box-shadow 的效果:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shadowColor <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"rgba(0,0,0,0.2)\"</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shadowBlur <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">20</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shadowOffsetX <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shadowOffsetY <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"ctx.createLinearGradient","date":"2020/07/15","slug":"about-canvas-ctx-createLinearGradient","description":null}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"about-canvas-ctx-createLinearGradient"}}}